    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "pp_text",
      "x": 75,
      "y": 145,
      "width": 250,
      "height": 160,
      "text": "1. Robust Scaling\n   median + IQR (not mean + std)\n   \u2192 resistant to outliers\n\n2. Smooth Clipping\n   soft clip instead of hard cutoff\n   \u2192 preserves gradient flow\n\n3. Piecewise-Linear Embeddings\n   learned 1D lookup per feature\n   \u2192 captures non-linearity pre-MLP",
      "originalText": "1. Robust Scaling\n   median + IQR (not mean + std)\n   \u2192 resistant to outliers\n\n2. Smooth Clipping\n   soft clip instead of hard cutoff\n   \u2192 preserves gradient flow\n\n3. Piecewise-Linear Embeddings\n   learned 1D lookup per feature\n   \u2192 captures non-linearity pre-MLP",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#374151",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
